# adversary-keys — one line per participant: username pubkey [comment]
# Copy to adversary-keys (gitignored) and add real public keys before deploying.
# For local dev, ./ctl up will add your own key for user 'ponder' automatically.
#
# ponder    ssh-ed25519 AAAA... participant1@team
# hex       ssh-ed25519 AAAA... participant2@team
# ridcully  ssh-ed25519 AAAA... participant3@team
# librarian ssh-ed25519 AAAA... participant4@team
# dean      ssh-ed25519 AAAA... participant5@team
